Enum LanguageType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LanguageType>
      • com.amplifyframework.predictions.models.LanguageType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LanguageType>

    public enum LanguageType
extends java.lang.Enum<LanguageType>
    Enum of different types of language. These are the languages that are recognized and supported by Amazon Translate Service and Amazon Comprehend Service.
    See Also:
    What is Amazon Translate?, Detect the Dominant Language
